---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import GitHubIcon from '../components/icons/GitHubIcon.astro';
import LinkedInIcon from '../components/icons/LinkedInIcon.astro';
import CalendarIcon from '../components/icons/CalendarIcon.astro';
import MailIcon from '../components/icons/MailIcon.astro';
import portraitImage from '../images/elkvtc.jpg';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Mike Cousins">
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-8 sm:py-20 lg:px-12">
    <p class="small-caps mb-6 text-[10px] text-flare-400 sm:text-xs">
      <span class="text-flare-500">◊</span> About
    </p>

    <header class="mb-16 grid gap-12 lg:mb-24 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-16">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <h1
          class="type-architecture font-extrabold text-ink-50"
          style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6.5vw, 5.5rem)"
        >
          I'm Mike. <span class="text-ink-500"
            >I live in Calgary, where I help companies start and scale.</span
          >
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:pt-2">
        <div
          class="relative aspect-[4/5] w-full overflow-hidden bg-flare-500"
        >
          <Image
            src={portraitImage}
            alt="Mike, with the rowing crew on a fall lake."
            widths={[400, 600, 900, 1200]}
            sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 33vw"
            class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover grayscale contrast-110 mix-blend-multiply"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-flare-500 mix-blend-color opacity-85"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-16">
      <div class="prose-mike lg:col-span-8">
        <p>
          I started my life in the shadow of my father, a career software
          developer and ravenous learner. He inspired my love of computers and
          all kinds of technology. I had a computer in my bedroom by the time
          I was 6, and I began exploring it day and night.
        </p>
        <p>
          After school I set off on a mission to work in as many different
          industries as possible. This is one of my favourite aspects of
          technology, the ability to work in any industry. Since then I have
          worked in telecommunications, oil and gas, healthcare, finance,
          energy, and many more.
        </p>
        <p>
          I have also done many different roles at those companies from being
          a pure software developer, to architecting and tech leadership, all
          the way up to CTO/VP roles. I still don't know what I like best, so
          I keep doing them all. Maybe when I get older I'll figure it out.
        </p>
        <p>
          Along the way I have realized that I love small companies, as I find
          that I get the most opportunities to make a real impact. I usually
          get a widely defined role where I get to touch a lot of the
          business. True happiness for me is learning about a new business, a
          new industry, meeting new people, and getting to solve a fun
          problem.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today, I am tackling as many problems as I can get my hands on. I
          usually have a few things going on at all times to keep me busy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="lg:col-span-4 lg:border-l lg:border-ink-800 lg:pl-8">
        <p class="small-caps mb-5 text-[10px] text-ink-400">
          <span class="text-flare-400">▸</span> Reach me
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a
              href="mailto:mike@cousins.ai"
              class="group inline-flex items-baseline gap-3 text-ink-100 transition-colors hover:text-flare-400"
            >
              <MailIcon
                className="h-4 w-4 fill-current relative top-[2px] text-flare-500 group-hover:text-flare-400"
              />
              mike@cousins.ai
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://cal.com/mikecousins"
              class="group inline-flex items-baseline gap-3 text-ink-100 transition-colors hover:text-flare-400"
            >
              <CalendarIcon
                className="h-4 w-4 fill-current relative top-[2px] text-flare-500 group-hover:text-flare-400"
              />
              Book a meeting
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/mikecousins"
              class="group inline-flex items-baseline gap-3 text-ink-100 transition-colors hover:text-flare-400"
            >
              <GitHubIcon
                className="h-4 w-4 fill-current relative top-[2px] text-flare-500 group-hover:text-flare-400"
              />
              github.com/mikecousins
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mikecousins"
              class="group inline-flex items-baseline gap-3 text-ink-100 transition-colors hover:text-flare-400"
            >
              <LinkedInIcon
                className="h-4 w-4 fill-current relative top-[2px] text-flare-500 group-hover:text-flare-400"
              />
              linkedin.com/in/mikecousins
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
